---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'July 15, 2026';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="How mikemurphy.ai collects, uses, and protects your information." canonical="/privacy-policy/">
  <main class="mm-container py-16">
    <p class="mm-eyebrow">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="mm-h1 mt-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mm-lede mt-5">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="mm-prose prose mt-8 max-w-3xl">
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how mikemurphy.ai ("the Site," "we," "us," or
        "our") collects, uses, and protects information when you visit the Site
        or subscribe to our newsletter, AI Unplugged.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3>Newsletter Signup</h3>
      <p>
        When you subscribe to AI Unplugged, we collect your email address (and
        any other information you voluntarily provide, such as your name).
        Newsletter delivery and subscriber management are handled by our email
        service provider, Beehiiv. Beehiiv processes this information on our
        behalf and maintains its own privacy practices, which you can review at
        Beehiiv's privacy policy. We do not sell or rent your email address to
        third parties.
      </p>

      <h3>Analytics</h3>
      <p>
        We use analytics tools (such as Google Analytics or a comparable
        service) to understand how visitors use the Site — for example, which
        pages are viewed, how long visitors stay, and general geographic and
        device information. This data is aggregated and does not directly
        identify you. These tools may use cookies or similar technologies to
        collect this information.
      </p>

      <h3>Information You Provide Directly</h3>
      <p>
        If you contact us directly (for example, by email), we retain that
        correspondence and any information you choose to include in it.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Send the AI Unplugged newsletter to subscribers</li>
        <li>Understand and improve how visitors use the Site</li>
        <li>Respond to questions or messages you send us</li>
        <li>Maintain the security and proper functioning of the Site</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        The Site and its third-party tools (such as analytics and newsletter
        widgets) may use cookies or similar technologies. You can control
        cookies through your browser settings; disabling them may affect some
        site functionality.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        We use third-party services — including Beehiiv for newsletter
        delivery and an analytics provider for traffic reporting — that may
        collect information as described above. We are not responsible for the
        privacy practices of these third parties, and we encourage you to
        review their respective privacy policies.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights and Choices</h2>
      <p>
        You may unsubscribe from AI Unplugged at any time using the unsubscribe
        link included in every email, or by contacting us directly. Depending
        on where you live, you may have additional rights regarding your
        personal information, such as the right to request access to, or
        deletion of, the information we hold about you. To exercise any of
        these rights, contact us using the details below.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        The Site is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly
        collect personal information from children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be
        posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use
        of the Site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the
        revised policy.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this Privacy Policy can be sent to
        <a href="mailto:mike@mikemurphy.co">mike@mikemurphy.co</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
